    "description": "Singing karaoke in Discord, playing music in a game... do you get tired of those mixing consoles? Why not try Sumtune? It only takes three steps to set everything up.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Music through Your Mic</h2>Sumtune is an application that can mix the input voice with chosen audio sources and play it out in different applications, so your friends can hear it in real-time.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Three Steps to Setup</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230320/extras/c49d4251011adf67ec1e7b505bed55d9.poster.avif?t=1671429661\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230320/extras/c49d4251011adf67ec1e7b505bed55d9.webm?t=1671429661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230320/extras/c49d4251011adf67ec1e7b505bed55d9.mp4?t=1671429661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Select the microphone that you are currently using.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230320/extras/ea547e9b7a060d39fb3d4ed328567ec9.poster.avif?t=1671429661\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230320/extras/ea547e9b7a060d39fb3d4ed328567ec9.webm?t=1671429661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230320/extras/ea547e9b7a060d39fb3d4ed328567ec9.mp4?t=1671429661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose the application of your audio sources. Some examples are Spotify, Potplayer, and Chrome.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230320/extras/2f84eb784601b312dd23452a74b2c754.poster.avif?t=1671429661\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230320/extras/2f84eb784601b312dd23452a74b2c754.webm?t=1671429661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230320/extras/2f84eb784601b312dd23452a74b2c754.mp4?t=1671429661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use the Sumtune microphone as your input device in those applications where you want to share the audio.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Notes</h2>When you run Sumtune for the first time, it will install the virtual microphone for you.",
